out, help out almost

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:13.610
like in a camping
trip environment,

00:06:13.610 --> 00:06:17.490
and came back a completely--
not changed person,

00:06:17.490 --> 00:06:20.670
but really a broadened person.

00:06:20.670 --> 00:06:23.120
I'm always fascinated
by the insight that

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:27.990
comes from a person, an
idea, a company, a brand that

00:06:27.990 --> 00:06:33.100
can open up people emotionally
and get them to connect.

00:06:33.100 --> 00:06:35.710
